name: Stephany Gonzalez
description:
Stephany Gonzalez, fitness and Instagram model.

Recently, one of my favorite author @JernauGurgeh posted a TI with her. He inspired me to try my version. I tried very hard to convey not only her facial features, but also her amazing fitness shape. I hope I succeeded)

I hope someone likes it I will be glad to hear any feedback!

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: Stephany Gonzalez is a fitness model from Venezuela. I really like her, so I decided to make a new, more stable and flexible version. Completely retrained model from scratch. I got good results even without reduces the weight.
